data.description: 3 bed + Office on 1 acre with a 40x60 steel shop. Right outside Winter Creek Golf Course in the Acreage Addition. Open floor plan with large foyer. Farmhouse accents. Gas fireplace in the living. Granite counter tops throughout. Open kitchen with island, gas range, open shelving, farm sink & pantry (Fridge stays!). Large master bedroom with patio access & accent wall. Master bath has large walk in shower, double vanities with make-up area, & privacy toilet. Master closet with connected to laundry room. Barn door entry to study/office. Hall bath with dual vanities & privacy shower. Laundry with mud bench & folding area. Insulated garage doors. Security system stay. Covered porch. Partial guttering. Large covered patio with lighting. Gas connection available for grill. Shop has 2- 8x10 over head doors, concrete floors, & electric. Water well. Aerobic system. Propane. OEC fiber available. Grady County. Middleburg & Blanchard schools (within 6 miles). 14 miles to Newcastle, OK. 18 miles to Norman, OK.
